SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1/DEBC, :1/DEBH where DEBC_ADMNO= :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBC_DATDELETED is null and DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH and DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = ':4' and DEBC_DEBC <>'0' and DEBC_DEBC <> '' for fetch only

select count(*) from :1/DEBC, :1/DEBH where DEBC_ADMNO= :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBC_DATDELETED is null and DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH and DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = ':4' and DEBC_LEGALCOLLECTION = 'Y' for fetch only

select count(*), cast(sum(DEBC_CREDITLIMITH) as decimal (11,0)) from :1/DEBC, :1/DEBH where DEBC_ADMNO= :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBC_DATDELETED is null and DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH and DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = ':4' and DEBC_CREDITLIMITH > 0 and DEBC_OWNJUDGLIMIT = 'N' for fetch only

select count(*), cast(sum(DEBC_CREDITLIMITH) as decimal (11,0)) from :1/DEBC, :1/DEBH where DEBC_ADMNO= :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBC_DATDELETED is null and DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH and DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = ':4' and DEBC_CREDITLIMITH > 0 and DEBC_OWNJUDGLIMIT = 'Y' for fetch only

select count(*), cast(sum(DEBC_FINANCELIMITH) as decimal (11,0)) from :1/DEBC, :1/DEBH where DEBC_ADMNO= :2 and DEBC_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBC_DATDELETED is null and DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH and DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = ':4' and DEBC_FINANCELIMITH > 0 for fetch only

select count(*) from :1/DEBB, :1/DEBC, :1/DEBH where DEBB_ADMNO= :2 and DEBB_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBB_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and DEBB_ACTINVAH <> 0 and DEBC_DATDELETED is null and DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH and DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = ':4' for fetch only

select count(*), cast(sum(DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(DEBB_ACTINVASPECACCH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/DEBB where DEBB_ADMNO= :2 and DEBB_CLNTNO = :3 and DEBB_ACTINVAH <> 0 and (DEBB_ACTINVAH * 100 / :4) > :5 for fetch only
